The intercity trains from Shenzhen to Guangzhou depart every ten minutes. Passengers can take a CRH train from Shenzhen to Guangzhou at Shenzhen Railway Station. It is a 1-1.5 hour journey. Please see Shenzhen-Guangzhou train schedule on China Highlights to search for a train from Shenzhen to Guangzhou. Intercity trains from Shenzhen to Guangzhou depart every ten minutes.
